{"tid":2486942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒古思堯參與反蒙面法遊行 未經批准集結罪成 判囚4及5個月","createTime":"2021-04-13T08:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:16:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a047c557e541a13bbcbd207a53542de30e5bf500","tid":2486942,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"前年10月5日蒙面法生效首日，港島有市民上街抗議，由銅鑼灣遊行到中環。正因包圍警總案在囚的黃之鋒，早前承認參與未經批准集結和違反蒙面法，社運人士古思堯則於今早被裁定參與未經批准集結罪成。代表黃之鋒的大狀求情時強調，終審法院接納公民抗命行為，且當日遊行規模小。控方則引周庭包圍警總案例反駁，卻遭裁判官鄧少雄質疑嚴重程度不同。鄧官下午分別判黃入獄4個月，古入獄5個月。<br />\n<br />\n今早散庭後，黃之鋒返回羈留室，其間向旁聽市民說：「一陣間見，好掛住你哋呀！」支持者熱烈揮手，勉勵稱：「撐住呀！」<br />\n<br />\n控方向法庭呈交周庭包圍警總案例作參考。裁判官指該案與本案的嚴重程度有相當大分別，例如本案沒有暴力事件，也不是衝擊警總之類標誌性建築物，純粹遊行。控方澄清不是想比較兩案，只是想援引案例列出的判刑考慮因素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/ZRJRO22GRBE6PJQFJ2DONOV2A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FZRJRO22GRBE6PJQFJ2DONOV2A4%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=12ca6c38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FZRJRO22GRBE6PJQFJ2DONOV2A4%2F&h=e446420e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/ZRJRO22GRBE6PJQFJ2DONOV2A4/</a>"},{"pid":"a5466c8d1eb8a82321630164990d09166ba3c50e","tid":2486942,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:22:16.000Z","msg":"之鋒仲有單47人案未審"},{"pid":"33abe9e632f01e92537a3045057d6f02ef7c222b","tid":2486942,"uid":311611,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:22:22.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒 多謝你俾機會我地班BNO撚移民. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d516fbcf9b6d38d77ee20273e6384d846d4080","tid":2486942,"uid":191579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:24:24.000Z","msg":"係擔心之後條國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705ab78644f63af0db64c75c9ebad9e8f8da081d","tid":2486942,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"古思堯又要入番去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d9d7384ff13108715d0d33690ac5d595c42000","tid":2486942,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5466c8d1eb8a82321630164990d09166ba3c50e","tid":2486942,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:22:16.000Z","msg":"之鋒仲有單47人案未審"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"果個好似用國安法拉,有排冇得見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa010de78c326be959b88c4b79136b5934ee1d1d","tid":2486942,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14993&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=9ce48257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14993</a><br />\n<br />\nD1 鄧官前再確認承認兩控罪❗️<br />\n-就非法集結律師求情引用2014-16年葉寶琳，黃毓民等案例判以罰款。本案是和平集結，沒暴力元素，為時兩三小時。但鄧官回應有預計包括準備banner及直幡。至於第二控罪，律師指庭上片段可見黃最初沒有戴口罩，只是遊行時接受記者訪問後才戴上，用意不是隱藏身份，只是示威表達公民抗命。<br />\n<br />\nD2古 經審訊後裁決罪名成立❗️❗️<br />\n<br />\n控方希望法庭依賴2013年古思堯燒國旗一案，當時不認罪，但沒有挑戰控方案情，沒有浪費法庭時間。法官問被告求情有沒有嘢講，古說自己有第四期癌症需治療，但仍會配合法庭及懲教準備第十一次坐監，唔希望法庭同情，可憐。<br />\n<br />\n🔥判刑速報<br />\nD1 即時監禁4個月❗️❗️<br />\nD2 即時監禁5個月❗️❗️<br />\n<br />\n簡短判刑理由<br />\n控罪(1)參考周庭2020年一案，非法集結量刑以12個月起點。然而本案人數、時間及行為遠不及該案，法庭會以6個月作起點，D1認罪減去三份一即判處4個月。D2在審訊中沒有爭議案情扣減一個月。D1控罪(2)以15日作量刑起點，扣減三份一後與控罪(1)同期執行<br />\n<br />\n📍兩位精神不錯，黃在欄內不時望向旁聽席，古上午完庭前呼「人權大於政權！人民大於國家！」。判刑離開時旁聽人士向兩人說加油💪"},{"pid":"2b81405caad827c0c88f2577a6db3aafa9007ab4","tid":2486942,"uid":136994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac29b86c9feb6e15bdc4b6b3f513c9f309d5a268","tid":2486942,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd6b12f6309dab94915273e68c8fa82cada7c17","tid":2486942,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eb2f7a29700e67ca8e5c1dbd5e55a0c3345d1e","tid":2486942,"uid":220985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"政治法慘撚到 古思堯啱啱先出咗嚟係咪？。。"},{"pid":"37c25e80d14bfac2da81d84d4933516c9b2b4df2","tid":2486942,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />參考周庭2020年一案"},{"pid":"cb639dcc71adc0d733c974fca59bf73ae608d1ca","tid":2486942,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffd6b12f6309dab94915273e68c8fa82cada7c17","tid":2486942,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"b264940cc8475dafa9e61159dd56b5eb1377fedc","tid":2486942,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"關公：都未L驚過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bcdcaadf7d10031c8e2968c8cd862d8201e68b","tid":2486942,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cd83cf44de30c35c9586409d3c7517d4ba7a92","tid":2486942,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705ab78644f63af0db64c75c9ebad9e8f8da081d","tid":2486942,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"古思堯又要入番去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:39:09.000Z","msg":"民族英雄  曾經"},{"pid":"31231a13b5adf534ac862330f88190fe65e67560","tid":2486942,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"gphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222d7fffedd2ff571261e830f3ca8b13412d8170","tid":2486942,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"企開啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"b579798ca6fee8ea55ceea696234f72bbb8cd3ff","tid":2486942,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17d9d7384ff13108715d0d33690ac5d595c42000","tid":2486942,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5466c8d1eb8a82321630164990d09166ba3c50e","tid":2486942,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:22:16.000Z","msg":"之鋒仲有單47人案未審"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"果個好似用國安法拉,有排冇得見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"係終生監禁"},{"pid":"55a50b6cbdca8947a69a0a79bf6bcd7006c660c4","tid":2486942,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"仲有條黨安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d9f304c88aa79e54d927fe56e29c68099136c1","tid":2486942,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"又迫害gphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bf7aa0f9f78b76681dc08d493d354346fe4590","tid":2486942,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"周庭嗰單有約束力？"},{"pid":"ac635f5f8553b52ac8f4659a4af6249d912e9ca8","tid":2486942,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"裁判官判刑時表示，就參與未經批准集結一罪並無量刑指引，主要參考 2019 年 6 月 21 日前眾志成員周庭包圍警總一案，該案的量刑起點為 12 個月。惟裁判官認為，該案程度遠比本案龐大及嚴重。裁判官續指，黃之鋒於本案屬標誌性人物，而古思堯當日手扶直幡，事後亦將直幡折起收好，屬帶領性人物，故採取 6 個月為量刑起點。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官稱，黃之鋒除認罪外，並無其他減刑因素，就參與未經批准集結判處他監禁 4 個月，而就違反《禁蒙面法》判處監禁 10 日，兩項刑期同期執行，並與現有刑期分期執行，即黃之鋒在正服刑的 13.5 個月刑期外，另須監禁 4 個月。<br />\n<br />\n至於古思堯，裁判官稱他有 13 次定罪記錄，上訴庭亦有指出，其身體狀況不構成減刑因素，但考慮到古思堯對控方案情沒有重大爭議，因此酌情扣減一個月，判處他監禁 5 個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%AD%A3%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%8F%A4%E6%80%9D%E5%A0%AF%E7%94%AB%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9A-5-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E7%2594%25AB%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%259B%259A-5-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%2F&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=b1e90bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E7%2594%25AB%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%259B%259A-5-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%2F&h=24f95a17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%AD%A3%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%8F%A4%E6%80%9D%E5%A0%AF%E7%94%AB%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9A-5-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88/</a>"},{"pid":"ec653bbf8a78a2ee0d8b212fc588ddb89c45abd2","tid":2486942,"uid":388684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"今星期還有 818 未經批准集結判刑。"},{"pid":"c4d7503eeb188a295177f574b8a02b28d12dbdd9","tid":2486942,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}